+[Unit]
+Description=CypherClaw Generation Worker
+Documentation=file:///home/user/cypherclaw/docs/runbooks/generation-backend.md
+After=cypherclaw-jack.service network-online.target
+Requires=cypherclaw-jack.service
+Wants=network-online.target
